# Keep the build context tiny: only ship the dockerfile, frozen requirements,
# and the prebuilt wheels we COPY in to skip CUDA template compilation
# (causal-conv1d, flash_attn). Everything else (code, data, checkpoints) is
# uploaded per-job via submit_job.sh, not baked in.
*
!docker/Dockerfile
!docker/requirements.txt
!docker/wheels
!docker/wheels/*.whl
